'''库曼语'''是一种由[[库曼人|库曼人]]和[[钦察|钦察]]人使用的[[突厥语族|突厥语族]][[钦察语支|钦察语支]]语言；其与今日钦察-库曼语群的许多语言很相似。库曼语在许多中世纪文献中保存，如《库曼语手册》；以及一些近代手稿，如本笃会修士Johannes ex Grafing的笔记。<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Knauer |first1=Georg Nicholaus |title=The Earliest Vocabulary of Romani Words (c. 1515) in the Collectanea of Johannes ex Grafing, a student of Johannes Reuchlin and Conrad Celtis |journal=Romani Studies |date=2010 |volume=20 |issue=1 |pages=1–15 |doi=10.3828/rs.2010.1|s2cid=170292032 }}</ref>它曾是中东欧的有着大量文学遗产的书面语。后来成为[[金帐汗国|金帐汗国]][[通用语|通用语]]。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://old.unesco.kz/qypchaq/Memorials-En.htm|title=Turkic written memorials|website=Old.unesco.kz|access-date=2019-07-27|archive-date=2018-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181013095659/http://old.unesco.kz/qypchaq/Memorials-En.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==历史==
[[image:Codex_Cumanicus_001.jpg|thumb]]
库曼人是在[[金帐汗国|金帐汗国]]前分布在[[东欧|东欧]]草原、[[黑海|黑海]]北岸的游牧民族。包括[[克里米亚鞑靼人|克里米亚鞑靼人]]、[[卡拉恰伊人|卡拉恰伊人]]、[[库梅克人|库梅克人]]和[[巴尔卡尔人|巴尔卡尔人]]在内的许多突厥民族都是库曼人的后裔。今日，使用这些语言的民族属于[[钦察语支|钦察]]-库曼语支，语言和库曼语关系密切。

库曼语在[[匈牙利王国|匈牙利王国]]库曼尼亚地区于17世纪早期变得濒危。一般认为最后一名库曼语母语者是以斯帖·瓦罗，是[[考尔曹格|考尔曹格]]居民，死于1770年。

库曼-钦察人曾在[[哈萨克斯坦|哈萨克斯坦]]、[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]、[[格鲁吉亚|格鲁吉亚]]、[[匈牙利|匈牙利]]、[[罗马尼亚|罗马尼亚]](如[[巴萨拉布王朝|巴萨拉布王朝]])、[[摩尔多瓦|摩尔多瓦]]、[[比萨拉比亚|比萨拉比亚]]和[[保加利亚|保加利亚]]的历史上有着重要地位。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://medium.com/bahasantara/sun-language-theory-part-2-the-steppes-of-tartary-tatar-bashkir-kazakh-kyrgyz-acfe3793938b|title=Sun Language Theory, Part 2: The Steppes of Tartary (Tatar, Bashkir, Kazakh, Kyrgyz)|last=Sun|first=Kevin|date=2019-04-07|website=Medium|language=en|access-date=2019-09-17|archive-date=2019-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191214010635/https://medium.com/bahasantara/sun-language-theory-part-2-the-steppes-of-tartary-tatar-bashkir-kazakh-kyrgyz-acfe3793938b|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==语例==
《库曼语手册》中一段库曼钦察突厥语[[主祷文|主祷文]]如下：

{{quote|{{lang|qwm|Atamız kim köktesiñ. Alğışlı bolsun seniñ atıñ, kelsin seniñ xanlığıñ, bolsun seniñ tilemekiñ – neçik kim kökte, alay [da] yerde. Kündeki ötmegimizni bizge bugün bergil. Dağı yazuqlarımıznı bizge boşatqıl – neçik biz boşatırbız bizge yaman etkenlerge. Dağı yekniñ sınamaqına bizni quurmağıl. Basa barça yamandan bizni qutxarğıl. Amen!}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://archive.org/details/codexcumanicusbi00kuunuoft|title=Kuun, Géza et al.: Codex cumanicus, Bibliothecae ad templum divi Marci Venetiarum primum ex integro editit prolegomenis notis et compluribus glossariis instruxit comes Géza Kuun, Budapest 1880, XLIX|website=Archive.org|access-date=2016-08-11}}</ref>}}

在[[乌古斯语支|乌古斯语支]]或更西的[[土耳其语|土耳其语]]中同一段文本写作：

{{quote|{{lang|tr|Atamız ki göktesin. Alkışlı olsun senin adın, gelsin senin hanlığın, olsun senin dilediğin – nice ki gökte, öyle de yerde. Gündelik ekmeğimizi bize bugün ver. Günahlarımızı bağışla – nice ki bağışlarız biz, bize yamanlık edenleri. Ve bizi kötülüğün sınamasından kurtar. Tüm yamandan bizi kurtar. Amin!}}}}

